  <heading>LDFF1SH (vector plus immediate)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>Gather load first-fault signed halfwords to vector (immediate index)</brief>
    <description>
      <para>Gather load with first-faulting behavior of signed halfwords to active elements of a vector register from memory addresses generated by a vector base plus immediate index. The index is a multiple of 2 in the range 0 to 62. Inactive elements will not read Device memory or signal faults, and are set to zero in the destination vector.</para>
    </description>
    <status>Green</status>
    <predicated>True</predicated>
  </desc>
